。 同时，30-34岁人群占比达到了20%，比上一年提升了0.7个百分点，连续两年超过20-24岁人群成为占比第二高的年龄段，比2005年提升了10.1个百分点；35-39岁人群占比达到了8.7%，比上一年提升了0.4个百分点，比2005年提升了3.8个百分点；40岁以上人群占比达到19.5%。 总体看，30-34岁和35-39岁这两个年龄段的占比都创下了近年来的新高。若以30岁为界来看，30岁以及以上人群占比合计达到了48.2%，比上一年度提高了1.7个百分点，创下了新高。整体而言，我国结婚年龄越来越迟。结婚人数首次低于800万对，超30岁结婚人群占比近半"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ip5np+ZGih4ErEAMaCDg0NjgwOTY3IOXqtpgGMAM4S0AWcgk1NTA3ODc1NzZ4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"92 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":"https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-5fbd19c431645e5756ab748321685116_1440w.png"}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"23_1661857923.5358243","card_id":"Q_549450754","target":{"id":549450754,"title":"17w研究所和27w私企怎么选？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/549450754","type":"question","created":1661137654,"answer_count":37,"follower_count":73,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[6391,9780,27713,48774,138952],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":"坐标陕西，专业交通。家在陕西，之前签了家一个研究所（17w，带编制，福利可能较好），前几天万集给了意向（保底13薪，月21k，在北京，可能解决北京户口）作息hr说的都是朝8晚6，双休。 ps：家境一般，去北京肯定无法买房"},"attached_info":"Cj4Ip5np+ZGih4ErEAMaCDg0MzgzODg5IPbli5gGMAA4SUAXcgk1NDk0NTA3NTR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"91 万热度","trend":0,"debut":true,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"24_1661857923.5365057","card_id":"Q_546719500","target":{"id":546719500,"title":"男朋友父亲只是个科员，要继续谈下去吗？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/546719500","type":"question","created":1659495705,"answer_count":678,"follower_count":879,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[3226,4729,26438,163085],"comment_count":52,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"ClUIp5np+ZGih4ErEAMaCDgzNzc2MzUxIJnKp5cGMDQ47